99
00:06:39,966 --> 00:06:41,991
Meredith, what a surprise.

100
00:06:42,168 --> 00:06:44,193
I figured we're actually
getting along today...

101
00:06:44,303 --> 00:06:45,998
why not push our luck.

102
00:06:46,105 --> 00:06:50,041
